{"tid":2249472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"睇隔離post話馬田比人屌得好勁扮慘帶風向 我笑撚左","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T03:35:50.000Z","uid":306055,"like":15,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"041b92c2ac3f513ee76e03a7a7bda5cdf42e8a62","tid":2249472,"uid":306055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"話咩d人個個屌馬田屌得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係度扮可憐扮慘<br />\n話人針對馬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd連登post一講兩句馬田壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬狗衝曬出黎幾百個負評：<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">分化狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫紅資滲透 其實係賺錢洗落黃圈 情有可原<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">得罪講句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />牛旨5粒丸都買$30<br />\n咁撚多馬狗課金 賺咁撚多<br />\n成班馬狗仲夠膽話馬田係迫不得已先賣紅資</span></span><br />\n話人雙重標準嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫達哥ming仔平反未？<br />\n牽涉到你就連登雙重標準好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔關馬狗事就ming狗達狗死撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe8cf3101fc49c601e01c3b5d12e03c1c93fce0","tid":2249472,"uid":306055,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"雙重標準撚唔夠馬狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達哥ming仔話自己淺黃 再幫tvb拍片<br />\n馬狗：屌你老母死賤種 <br />\n幫cctvb 死撚開啦ming狗達狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達ming一派狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫藍店<br />\n<br />\n馬田幫紅底公司滲透宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬狗：唔該唔好鬥黃😅🙏🏻<br />\n分化撚死開唔該😅🙏🏻<br />\n雖然牛旨賺咁撚多<br />\n但係接支那公司job 一定係賺藍店錢洗落黃圈😅🙏🏻"},{"pid":"5e37940ca9683826f4c5cee115d0093cdc700cdd","tid":2249472,"uid":306055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"sorry連登無動物傳心師的<br />\n馬狗d ig post無人知佢up乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1def58266008a1ef871179e463a2afa5f2f8169a","tid":2249472,"uid":306055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"馬狗fans眼中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬田做乜9都情有可原 事出有因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neven到時賣港撐共 都可以講成忍辱負重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真牛旨賺咁撚柒多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />5粒丸都賣三十幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都夠膽話唔夠錢所以接支那job"},{"pid":"3832710a4fb29a30b56117131ce5ffa74dedd566","tid":2249472,"uid":306055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" c